lockquote><blockquote>乜香港人對<del>馬路職業司機既</del>香港人格仲有期望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n喂"},{"pid":"b3cc8bcd5a8a79fc028c20bb27fac36a2bc6d7d3","tid":478369,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"女人渣車"},{"pid":"bff4a2c72e998e936c288545ddd42e95b6dba1cf","tid":478369,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女車長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae9c88802e6017378bc9d86bff5818cd9b27e02","tid":478369,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36e7cc1c6b7be25aaf9ccad98e0a42b233e659e","tid":478369,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"一部往屯門良景邨的58X駛至彌敦道789號健峯保險大廈對開巴士站，埋站上落客後正準備駛離巴士站，惟中線一部往長青的41號線九巴駛至，車長疑見58X未駛走，欲抽頭切往慢線行駛；不料，此時58X卻同時起步欲切出中線，兩九巴叮噹馬頭互不相讓，停在馬路中，兩車長更為此發生爭執。<br />\n<br />\n58x 同 41 落咗客喺燈位前分別行定中線同慢線係合理<br />\n因為58x 係唔會喺慢線嘅楓樹街個站 (即永亨銀行個球場停, 而要等到去黃竹街先上落客)<br />\n而41 就需要喺楓樹街上下客<br />\n<br />\n按返58x 喺太子站個位係前過41<br />\n即41 理應過咗站<br />\n而亦冇諗過原本咁停咁耐嘅58x 咁快上哂客<br />\n先咁啱有爭執<br />\n<br />\n其實邊個讓邊個先根本冇問題<br />\n總有一個要行先<br />\n除非前面有車頂住啫<br />\n<br />\n根本兩個司機都on9 兼小氣"},{"pid":"101cb0a145086877664da5fa922b1bf53618260d","tid":478369,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今鋪我撐司機啦<br />\n間唔中要搞下呢d野<br />\n攬炒下先得</blockquote><br />\nWhat for<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}